sections.heading: 45-1,105 to 45-1,110 shall apply to all consumer credit transactions in this state subject to a security interest, as defined in subdivision (35) of section 1-201, Uniform Commercial Code, entered into, extended, or renewed on or after January 1, 1984
sections.text: 45-1,105 to 45-1,110 shall apply to all consumer credit transactions in this state subject to a security interest, as defined in subdivision (35) of section 1-201, Uniform Commercial Code, entered into, extended, or renewed on or after January 1, 1984.
